Huatai Insurance Opens Branch in Shanghai
SHANGHAI , November 19 ( Xinhua ) -- The Huatai Insurance Co. , Ltd , the first Chinese shareholding property insurer , opened a branch in Shanghai today .
President of the company Wang Zimu said at the opening ceremony of the Huatai Shanghai branch that Shanghai is a standard insurance market for both Chinese and foreign insurers .
He said that Huatai Insurance 's shareholders include more than 63 large state-owned enterprises , and that its premium income last year reached 180 million yuan .
The insurer 's total assets are now valued at over 1.6 billion yuan .
It is expected that other foreign-funded insurance companies will also open offices soon in Shanghai .
